        <para id="id4265857">Learner 3:</para>
        <para id="id3504862">Design: </para>
        <para id="id4212662"/>
        <para id="id4104904"> Sketch and planning of container for electric circuit in isometric. Indicate the tessellation pattern and use an isometric grid.</para>
        <para id="id3247858">Design the net of the container/box on A3 graph paper.</para>
